review:
My 18 month old can work this and he and his 4.5yr old sister fight over 
who gets to play. It's great, but if the game with the train, and the 
vegetable tractor one could have their drop area extended that would be 
helpful. Some of them are very particular about where on the box you have 
to release for it to go in, allowing for the top and side would make for 
less frustration. (Little one likes to try put the veges over the outline 
on the side of the tractor for example)
Name: toddler-games-for-2-year-olds
